title: Did the military team play "Hit the Jack Road" outside the White House?
subtitle: A lot of social media chanted for what looked like the epic dwarf of the then American President Donald Trump.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: Before the inauguration of President-elect Joe Biden in January 2020, in 2021, the military squad conducted the "Jack Road Strike" outside the White House, where then President Donald Trump was still a resident.
